{"tid":1293833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方唔克制驅散示威者：認X住我呀！隻揪呀！","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:46:56.000Z","uid":48093,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"813a34eccf914f642d7ff3b2ff8da775fcdb6c58","tid":1293833,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190708/large/1562517875_7557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190708%2Flarge%2F1562517875_7557.jpg&h=964a1637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方晚上於旺角彌敦道驅散示威者，其中有一條片段在telegram群組流傳，清楚見到有警員驅散示威者期間，一名年約20歲的男子絆倒在地上，在場示威人士不齒警方強硬驅散，於是破口大罵，但警員竟然沒有克制，大聲呼喝：「咩呀！」，之後雙方不斷推撞，有警員更指：「認X住我呀」「隻揪呀」，意圖令示威者的不滿情緒加劇。"},{"pid":"6d571e47998b9c49971cbd6b1f1b92c1fccc83c7","tid":1293833,"uid":131157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1e6cc5b561c1de4111007a764b0ab448117a23","tid":1293833,"uid":58863,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"EQ咁撚低<br />\n肯定成撚日谷住谷住<br />\n谷到個頭都禿撚哂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c5c292f2e19b0b9e75002ca9ae7e105bef7a9e","tid":1293833,"uid":204565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"813a34eccf914f642d7ff3b2ff8da775fcdb6c58","tid":1293833,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledail